{
  "chapter": 19,
  "chapter_summary": "第十九章“杀与不杀”讲述萧秋水凭暴涨的内力连杀何狮、安判官、铁判官、康庭四大高手，与康出渔对掌占据绝对上风后康出渔逃走。曾森被迫带路至权力帮联络处“欢乐栈”。客栈内，火王祖金殿押送被擒的唐方、唐朋和欧阳珊一，祖金殿残暴凌辱欧阳珊一、烧伤劝阻的盛江北。萧秋水押曾森进入客栈却未识破伪装的唐方，后追击柳有孔而出。在死巷中击杀柳有孔和钟无离，因彭九之恩饶恕吴明。吴明告知人质信息，萧秋水恍悟唐方就在客栈，飞身赶回却发现人去楼空，曾森已被祖金殿烧死。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": "康出渔",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“你这小子来得好，我找你好久了……”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zeng_sen",
      "speaker_name": "曾森",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“他妈的你小子是什么人？”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_pan_guan",
      "speaker_name": "安判官",
      "listener": "char_zeng_sen",
      "text": "“他是成都浣花剑派萧西楼的儿子！”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_shi",
      "speaker_name": "何狮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“管他是谁的儿子，打死便了！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_shi",
      "speaker_name": "何狮",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“你小子——！”",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": "康出渔",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“你功力进步得好快呀！”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "text": "“少假惺惺！”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zeng_sen",
      "speaker_name": "曾森",
      "listener": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "text": "“他真的是萧秋水？”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": "康出渔",
      "listener": "char_zeng_sen",
      "text": "“那也没什么，”",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "speaker_name": "康出渔",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“你接我一掌试试！”",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_ting",
      "speaker_name": "康庭",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“好！”",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_ting",
      "speaker_name": "康庭",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“不妙！”",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zeng_sen",
      "speaker_name": "曾森",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“你要找死，快让路！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zeng_sen",
      "text": "“我是找死，你就给我死吧！”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zeng_sen",
      "speaker_name": "曾森",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“我俩无怨无仇，何必苦苦相逼！”",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zeng_sen",
      "text": "“刚才你们有六个人的时候，为何不说这句话？”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zeng_sen",
      "speaker_name": "曾森",
      "listener": "char_kang_chu_yu",
      "text": "“康老师——救命——”",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zeng_sen",
      "text": "“你们这里的联络处在哪里？！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zeng_sen",
      "speaker_name": "曾森",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“别动手、别动手，我、我带您去。”",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zeng_sen",
      "text": "“你知道康出渔躲到哪里去吗？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zeng_sen",
      "speaker_name": "曾森",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“我可以带你去——在下也不知他，他是不是到那儿去，但那儿确是权力帮在这边的联络处……”",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zeng_sen",
      "text": "“解下你的弯刀——你带我去，我便饶你不杀！”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "speaker_name": "祖金殿",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_shan_yi",
      "text": "“你有身孕，对我来说连做那事儿也不方便……难得你出落是那么漂亮，就赏给那些有兴趣的弟兄们玩玩吧。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "盛江北",
      "listener": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "text": "“既然这女人已有身孕，丈夫也给杀了，不如就放了她算吧。”",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "speaker_name": "祖金殿",
      "listener": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "text": "“你怜香借玉？哦？我喜欢干什么，就干什么，用不着你这老鬼劝说！”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_jiang_bei",
      "speaker_name": "盛江北",
      "listener": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "text": "“是。”",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "康劫生",
      "listener": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "text": "“启禀火王，属下对这女人，很有兴趣……”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "speaker_name": "祖金殿",
      "listener": "char_kang_jie_sheng",
      "text": "“你杀了她的丈夫，正是有功，合当你去亭用，哈哈哈……”",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "speaker_name": "祖金殿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“此人留不得，你带钟无离、柳有孔去把他千掉。”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "speaker_name": "祖金殿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“盛江北、左常生、康劫生，你三人先避一避。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“是。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zeng_sen",
      "speaker_name": "曾森",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“他们、他们……应汇聚在这里的。”",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“哦”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "speaker_name": "祖金殿",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "“叫了也没用，他若过来，马上就死，他不过来，一样死在外面，如此而已。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“钟无离！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "speaker_name": "钟无离",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“你好吧？这是咱们的第三次会面了。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_zhong_wu_li",
      "text": "“你——！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“轰！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "“你叫什么名字？”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“我叫吴明，……”",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "“你是彭九的人？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“是，是，我是彭九的弟子。”",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "“彭九对我有恩，我不杀你。”",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“谢——”",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“你放了我。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming",
      "text": "“你还不走？”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "吴明",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“我走，不过我先来告诉你一件事。在客店的那几个人，被我们所擒，‘火王’押送，其中二三人，像似你的朋友。你是来找他们的吧？话至此尽，告辞了。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19
    }
  ],
